stency. The resulting framework supports one-shot pose transfer, high-fidelity reenactment, and animation of unseen object categories (e.g., animals, furniture) with minimal fine-tuning. Potential impact spans digital avatars, virtual production, robotics simulation, and video editing, where robust, generalizable motion control is essential. By decoupling motion interpretation from geometric deformation through learned correspondence, CAT-Transformer opens a new direction in parametric-model-free neural scene animation.",
